  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Dose Received by the Prostate With in Vivo Dosimetry in Patients Treated With Daily IGRT Associated With IMRT Using Two Repositioning Techniques for Localized Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>PROSTRACK</acronym>
